Package de.adorsys.datasafe.privatestore.api.actions

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EncryptedResourceResolver
    Resolves logical resource location into encrypted absolute location and vice-versa.
    ListPrivate
    Lists user files in privatespace.
    ReadFromPrivate
    Reads users' file in privatespace.
    RemoveFromPrivate
    Removes users' file from privatespace.
    WriteToPrivate
    Writes to file in user privatespace.
